    "description": "README\n\n# Monitor Competitor Facebook Ads with Airtop\n\n## Use Case\n\nMonitor a competitor‚Äôs active Facebook ads and get a weekly HTML intelligence brief by email ‚Äî saving time on manual research and helping you spot messaging, offers, and creative trends quickly.\n\n## What This Automation Does\n\n* Runs weekly on a set schedule.\n* Uses **Airtop** to visit the competitor‚Äôs Facebook Ad Library page and extract up to 30 active ads.\n* Summarizes each ad with key points: message, topic, CTA, duration active, language, target audience.\n* Sends the compiled HTML report via Gmail.\n\n## How It Works\n\n1. **Schedule Trigger** ‚Äì Fires once a week at the configured time.\n2. **Airtop Extraction** ‚Äì Loads the Ad Library URL and runs a prompt to extract and format the ads into HTML.\n3. **Email Delivery** ‚Äì Sends the HTML report to your specified recipient using Gmail.\n\n## Setup Requirements\n\n1. **Airtop API Key** ‚Äî [Generate here](https://portal.airtop.ai/api-keys).\n2. **Airtop Credential in n8n** ‚Äî Add your API key under ‚ÄúAirtop‚Äù in n8n.\n3. **Gmail OAuth2 Credential** ‚Äî Connect the Gmail account to send reports.\n4. **Competitor‚Äôs Ad Library URL** ‚Äî Replace the default `view_all_page_id` in the workflow with your target.\n\n## Next Steps\n\n* Duplicate the Airtop step for multiple competitors.\n* Enrich reports by visiting ad landing pages for deeper analysis.\n* Send outputs to Slack or archive in a shared workspace.\n\n[Read about ways to monitor your competitors ads here](https://www.airtop.ai/automations/competitor-facebook-ads-intelligence-agent-n8n)",
